'''先進戰鬥頭盔'''或'''先進作戰頭盔'''（{{lang-en|'''Advanced Combat Helmet'''}}），簡稱'''ACH頭盔'''，是[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]的現役[[戰鬥頭盔|戰鬥頭盔]]，由{{Link-en|美國陸軍士兵系統中心|United States Army Soldier Systems Center}}研發為美陸軍新一代的防護盔<ref>{{cite web| title= Advanced Combat Helmet ( ACH )| url= http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/systems/ground/ach.htm| accessdate= 2007-03-22| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070316075928/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/systems/ground/ach.htm| archivedate= 2007-03-16| deadurl= no}}</ref>，其設計為{{Link-en|MICH頭盔|Modular Integrated Communications Helmet}}的衍生。

== 歷史 ==
ACH頭盔在2003年首次由{{Link-en|美國士兵計劃執行室|PEO Soldier}}推出，用以取代1985年後持續使用的[[PASGT鋼盔|PASGT頭盔]]<ref name=44,000 />。

2007年時，美國陸軍引入一種後頸護墊裝置，附加在頭盔的後部位置，以防止士兵死於砲彈碎片的情形，在快速裝備計畫中預計發放43份後頸護墊裝置{{notetag|快速裝備計畫，{{lang-en|RFI，Rapid Fielding Initiative}}}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vimeo.com/4244876 |title=Rapid Fielding Initiative - Lean Fielding - Ft. Drum NY |access-date=2014-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202232651/http://vimeo.com/4244876 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.defensemedianetwork.com/stories/rapid-fielding-initiative/ Rapid Fielding Initiative - A decade of providing urgently needed gear]</ref><ref name=430,000 />。

2008年早期，{{Link-en|美國士兵計劃執行室|PEO Soldier|士兵計劃執行室}}將內嵌有感應器的頭盔供應給將前往[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]的[[第101空降師|第101空降師]]及[[美國陸軍第4步兵師|美國陸軍第4步兵師]]各部隊，以對[[土製炸彈|土製炸彈]]所致的頭部受傷事件蒐集相關數據，並利用這些數據改善MICH頭盔的設計<ref name="army.mil">{{Cite web |url=http://www.army.mil/-news/2008/06/03/9638-helmet-sensors-improved-armor-helping-soldier-survivability/ |title=Army.mil - Helmet Sensors, Improved Armor Helping Soldier Survivability |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2011-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211203629/http://www.army.mil/-news/2008/06/03/9638-helmet-sensors-improved-armor-helping-soldier-survivability/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年，自美國廠商{{Link-en|ArmorSource|ArmorSource}}訂購了102,000頂頭盔，其中99,000頂在合約完成後交貨。2009年5月時，該款頭盔的存貨有55,000頂，44,000頂供美國陸軍、[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]及[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]人員使用。但在2010年5月時，美國陸軍緊急回收全部44,000多頂鋼盔<ref>[http://tw.epochtimes.com/b5/10/5/16/n2909773.htm 大紀元 - 有瑕疵 美軍回收近5萬頂鋼盔] {{Wayback|url=http://tw.epochtimes.com/b5/10/5/16/n2909773.htm |date=20160304110035 }} - [[大紀元|大紀元]]台灣網</ref>，因為這些鋼盔可能使用了不符軍方品管標準的缺陷材質。但事後沒有證據證明缺陷材質存在，或是製造商有不法行為<ref name=44,000>{{cite web|title=Army recalls 44,000 helmets|url=http://www.armytimes.com/news/2010/05/army_helmet_recall_051410w/|publisher=Gannett Government Media Corporation|accessdate=31 January 2011|author=Matthew Cox|date=17 May 2010}}</ref>。

先前在2009年5月時，由美商{{Link-en|建泰公司|Gentex (military contractor)}}出產的34,218頂ACH頭盔即因未能在極端溫度下通過彈道測試而被回收，建泰公司宣稱其分包商杜撰了螺絲零件的證明書<ref name=44,000 />。同年晚期，開始替ACH頭盔加上[[MultiCam|MultiCam]]迷彩盔套，給美軍在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]的派遣部隊使用<ref>{{cite web|title=New uniform for OEF protects Soldiers, hides them better|url=http://www.army.mil/-news/2010/08/12/43570-new-uniform-for-oef-protects-soldiers-hides-them-better/|accessdate=31 January 2011|author=C. Todd Lopez|quote=Gear being fielded to Soldiers with the new pattern includes a cover for the Advanced Combat Helmet, the Extended Cold Weather Clothing System, the Fire Resistant Army Combat Uniform, the Improved Outer Tactical Vest, both the sun hat and patrol cap, name and service tapes for the FR ACU, and multiple pieces of Modular Lightweight Load-carrying Equipment.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204103529/http://www.army.mil/-news/2010/08/12/43570-new-uniform-for-oef-protects-soldiers-hides-them-better/|archivedate=2011年2月4日|deadurl=no|date=12 August 2010}}</ref>。

2011年1月13日，[[美國國防後勤局|美國國防後勤局]]額外向Revision Military下定了90000頂ACH頭盔，總價2100萬美元，每頂單價233美元。<ref>{{cite web|title=DLA orders additional advanced combat helmets from Revision|url=https://www.army-technology.com/news/newsadditional-advanced-combat-helmets-revision-4159831/}}</ref>

[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]在2011年與{{Link-en|建泰公司|Gentex (military contractor)}}簽約採購ACH<ref>{{cite web|title=U.S. MARINE CORP AWARDS GENTEX CORPORATION $53.5 MILLION CONTRACT|url=https://www.gentexcorp.com/u-s-marine-corp-awards-gentex-corporation-53-5-million-contract/|author=gentexcorp.com|date=30 Mar 2011}}</ref>，在2014年開始配發{{Link-en|建泰公司|Gentex (military contractor)}}生產的輕量化先進戰鬥頭盔 (Light Weight ACH)，同樣命名為[[輕量化頭盔|輕量化頭盔]](Lightweight Marine Corps Helmet)<ref>{{cite web|title=MDM – Gentex / Ops-Core|url=https://soldiersystems.net/2014/09/23/mdm-gentex-ops-core/|author=gentexcorp.com|date=23 Sep 2014}}</ref> ，由於採用了較新的[[克維拉|克維拉]]材料，在維持與舊型ACH相同防彈能力的同時厚度變得較薄，重量因此減輕了8% <ref>{{cite web|title=GENTEX CORPORATION ― GENTEX AWARDED $86.8M U.S. GOVERNMENT CONTRACT FOR LIGHTWEIGHT ADVANCED COMBAT HELMETS|url=https://www.gentexcorp.com/gentex-corporation-%e2%80%95-gentex-awarded-86-8m-u-s-government-contract-for-lightweight-advanced-combat-helmets/|author=gentexcorp.com|date=6 Sep 2013}}</ref>，主要配發{{Link-en|美國海軍陸戰隊偵察營|United States Marine Corps Reconnaissance Battalions}}和[[美國海軍陸戰隊武裝偵察部隊|美國海軍陸戰隊武裝偵察部隊]]。[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]則在2016春季開始配發10.5萬頂輕量化先進戰鬥頭盔，採用由ArmorSource生產的AS-505頭盔，L號的重量相比舊型ACH減輕了10%。<ref>{{cite web|title=ArmorSource to Provide 105,000 Lightweight Advanced Combat Helmets to the U.S. Army|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/armorsource-to-provide-105000-lightweight-advanced-combat-helmets-to-the-us-army-300199391.html|date=20 Jun 2019}}</ref>

[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]在2017年簽約採購293870頂Revision Military生產的ACH Gen II，預計在2022年3月6號前全部交付完畢，每頂單價334美元<ref>{{cite web|title=Revision Military awarded $98 million contract to produce combat helmets in Newport|url=https://newportdispatch.com/2017/03/21/revision-military-awarded-98-million-contract-produce-combat-helmets-newport/}}</ref>。由於採用了新的超高分子量聚乙烯(UHMWPE)材料，在維持與舊型ACH相同防彈能力的同時，各尺寸重量平均減少22%，最多減輕了24%<ref>{{cite web|title=PEO Soldier Talks About The Advanced Combat Helmet Gen II|url=https://soldiersystems.net/2017/03/30/peo-soldier-talks-helmets/|author=PEO Soldier|date=30 Mar 2017}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|title=ArmorSource to Provide 105,000 Lightweight Advanced Combat Helmets to the U.S. Army|url=https://govshop.com/media/opportunities/documents/2169615a914edd06346b456d09a9f15a20190620_ach_gen_ii_arpd_14-01c_amendment_1.pdf|author=ArmorSource LLC|date=2016-01-05}}</ref>。

[[美國陸軍|美國陸軍]]現有的ACH頭盔和{{translink|en|Enhanced Combat Helmet (United States)|增強型戰鬥頭盔}}預計會由{{translink|en|Integrated Head Protection System|整合頭部防護系統}}全面取代<ref>{{cite web|title=The Army’s new body armor and combat helmet are here. Here’s who will get them first|url=https://taskandpurpose.com/news/army-body-armor-combat-helmet/|author=JARED KELLER |date=7 Mar 2019}}</ref>。而[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]則由改良增強型戰鬥頭盔的高切增強型戰鬥頭盔(High-cut ECH)取代現有的ACH頭盔、[[輕量化頭盔|輕量化頭盔]]和舊型的增強型戰鬥頭盔<ref>{{cite web|title=Supporting the future fight: MCSC modernizing infantry capabilities|url=https://www.dvidshub.net/news/395823/supporting-future-fight-mcsc-modernizing-infantry-capabilities|author=Marine Corps Systems Command|date=6 May 2021}}</ref>。

== 設計 ==
ACH頭盔使用[[凱夫勒|凱夫勒]]及{{Link-en|特威龍|Twaron}}等彈道纖維作為材質<ref name=material>{{cite web|title=Army’s new plastic helmet tops Kevlar ACH|url=http://www.armytimes.com/news/2009/08/army_helmets_083109w/|publisher=Gannett Government Media Corporation|accessdate=31 January 2011|author=Matthew Cox|author2=Dan Lamothe|date=31 August 2009|deadurl=yes}}{{失效鏈接}}</ref>。防彈能力以17格令的模擬破片的V50標準值為2200英尺/秒(670米/秒)<ref>{{Cite web|title=PURCHASE DESCRIPTION HELMET, ADVANCED COMBAT (ACH) CO/PD-05-04|url=https://ciehub.info/spec/PD/CO-PD-05-04.pdf}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=PURCHASE DESCRIPTION HELMET, ADVANCED COMBAT (ACH) AR/PD-10-02|url=https://ciehub.info/spec/PD/AR-PD-10-02.pdf }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=PURCHASE DESCRIPTION HELMET, ADVANCED COMBAT, SECOND GENERATION (ACH GEN II) AR/PD 14-01 Rev C Amendment 1 |url=https://imlive.s3.amazonaws.com/Federal%20Government/ID12675891135242891056056689931107506559/20190620_ACH_Gen_II_ARPD_14-01C_Amendment_1.pdf }}</ref>。

2007年美國陸軍引進一種後頸護墊，附加在ACH頭盔的後部位置，以防止士兵死於砲彈碎片的情形<ref name=430,000>{{cite web|title=New helmet pad protects from fragments|url=http://www.armytimes.com/news/2007/02/ATnewhelmetpads070228/|publisher=Gannett Government Media Corporation|accessdate=31 January 2011|author=Matthew Cox|date=28 February 2007}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stripes.com/news/army-adding-neck-pad-to-body-armor-1.61148 |title=Stars and Stripes - Army Adding Neck Pad to Body Armor |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2012-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930064138/http://www.stripes.com/news/army-adding-neck-pad-to-body-armor-1.61148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時也引入了{{Link-en|改良型外部戰術背心|Improved Outer Tactical Vest}}（IOTV）。

